               <item corresp="#lb2" xml:space="preserve">
            <ref>1</ref>
            <p>
              The space available in the lacuna occurring at the end of the line seems not sufficient for a π̣[ρὸς] + acc. phrase. π̣[ᾶν ῥεῦμα]: see Gal.
              <emph rend="italics">Comp.med.sec.loc.</emph>
              4.8 (12, 748.13-4 K). π̣[ολὺ], or π̣[αχὺ ῥεῦμα], or π̣[ολλὰ ῥεύματα]: see Orib.
              <emph rend="italics">Syn</emph>
              . 3.139 (CMG 6.3, 103.16-7 Raed.) and 3.121 (CMG 6.3, 99.9 Raed.). π̣[εριωδυνίας]: Gal.
              <emph rend="italics">Comp.med.sec.loc.</emph>
              12, 743.15-6 K.
            </p>
            <p>περίχριστος (masculine) is less common than περίχριστον (neuter).</p>
          </item>
               <item corresp="#lb8" xml:space="preserve">
            <ref>4</ref>
            <p>
              ἴρεως: see
              <ref target="http://papyri.info/dclp/63118">P.Oxy. VIII 1088</ref>
              .34,
              <ref target="http://papyri.info/dclp/64507">O.Bodl. II 2184</ref>
              .5. [σ]μ̣ύ̣ρ̣ν̣[ης]: see Gal.
              <emph rend="italics">Comp.med.loc.</emph>
              XII 743.6ff. K.
            </p>
